{
  "id": "workflow-designer",
  "name": "Workflow Designer",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "firstParty": true,
  "description": "V6 shell 内置：/workflow 斜杠命令 + Home 页工作流设计快捷卡片（V5 WorkflowDesignerPage 的 V6 探针迁移）",
